T*
(enough. Sometimes a mention in a meeting is enough. Sometimes even a private message saying,) Tj
T*
(“I appreciated how you handled that situation” can go a long way.) Tj
T*
T*
(Recognition helps people feel seen. And when people feel seen, they usually become more) Tj
T*
