T*
T*
(So the culture becomes self-reinforcing.) Tj
T*
T*
(That is the kind of workplace we should aim for. Not just one where people complete tasks,) Tj
T*
(but one where knowledge is preserved, wisdom is transferred, people are valued, and everyone) Tj
T*
